content: Hi Taylor, I saw Gamma Solutions is in Houston and works in e-commerce. what is your current deployment process like-is it mostly manual or automated?
Who are you and why are you giving me a call?

Totally fair question. I’m Emma with Cloumen—we build AI-powered outreach that handles first-touch calls and qualification so teams like yours stay focused on real conversations. I’d never share anything you tell me; I’m only here to spot whether we can actually help. Would it be okay if I ask a quick question about how your team handles follow-ups or qualification? What’s been the biggest time sink lately?
Got it, thanks for letting me ask. What is your current deployment process like-is it mostly manual or automated?
Yeah, it is automated right now. We handle our calls through AI, we handle our lead generation through AI. So yeah, most of the things are automated right now.
I am having a connection issue. Can we try again in a moment?
I didn't get to repeat that again.
No worries at all, I know how frustrating tech hiccups can be. What time is best?
